    },
    {
      "type": "text", "id": "ev_trace_cmd_text", "x": 410, "y": 935, "width": 410, "height": 57,
      "text": "python .claude/scripts/code_graph trace Controller.cs \\\n  --direction both --node-mode file --json\n\n\u2192 Follows: CALLS + TRIGGERS_EVENT + MESSAGE_BUS + API_ENDPOINT\n\u2192 Shows full chain: Angular \u2192 Controller \u2192 Handler \u2192 Event \u2192 Bus \u2192 Consumer", "originalText": "python .claude/scripts/code_graph trace Controller.cs \\\n  --direction both --node-mode file --json\n\n\u2192 Follows: CALLS + TRIGGERS_EVENT + MESSAGE_BUS + API_ENDPOINT\n\u2192 Shows full chain: Angular \u2192 Controller \u2192 Handler \u2192 Event \u2192 Bus \u2192 Consumer",
      "fontSize": 9, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
